**EElOO and back:**

<iframe width="480" height="270" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ESRgUQ3SqzM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe>

Nice job getting a encounter back to kerbin so easily, I struggled for over an hour to do the same ! thats one trip I wont do again. 

how did you get gold parts by the way ?
That's kind of overkill for a rocket to Eeloo, don't you think? Or did you not have the Nuclear rockets yet?
